    • Method Detail

      • getRenderedFacetsAndChildren

        protected Iterator<javax.faces.component.UIComponent> getRenderedFacetsAndChildren(javax.faces.context.FacesContext facesContext)
        UIXShowDetail only allows processing of its children when it is disclosed. However ShowDetail has other facets like prompt etc that need to be processed even then it is not disclosed. So override the functionality from UIXShowDetail and pass it along to the default functionality where-in the renderer decides which children need to be processed
        Overrides:
        getRenderedFacetsAndChildren in class org.apache.myfaces.trinidad.component.UIXShowDetail
        Parameters:
        facesContext - the faces context.
        Returns:
        an iterator of UI components.
